onLineSrc.orDesc: Access to Washburn County GIS data

idCitation.otherCitDet: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use.

dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents parcels for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Washburn_Parcels_2015.gdb.
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
